{"id":621,"date":"2022-02-18T13:54:00","date_gmt":"2022-02-18T11:54:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=621"},"modified":"2022-03-23T21:48:55","modified_gmt":"2022-03-23T19:48:55","slug":"how-do-banks-innovate-and-grow-in-a-digital-age","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-do-banks-innovate-and-grow-in-a-digital-age\/","title":{"rendered":"How do Banks Innovate and Grow in a Digital Age?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>In the digital age FinTech startups are giving the <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-to-use-business-banking-for-online-business\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"454\">conventional banks<\/a> a run for their money, which is slowly bringing down the protective walls that were initially built by some of the largest financial institutions in the internet banking sector.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The onset of the digital age has caused a massive disruption in the finance industry with digital innovations in the wider <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/#:~:text=Anyone%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20business%20to%20a%20global%20scale%20should%20consider%20whether%20their%20current%20payment%20provider%20can%20handle%20such%20a%20shift\">payments<\/a> spectrum experiencing massive growth. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is especially attributed to the fact that millennials are currently the largest drivers of most economies. Here is how banks innovate and grow in this brave new world.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" area-label=\"ez-toc-toggle-icon-1\"><label for=\"item-673d664339719\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;alig